title: US march in 'not my Presidents' Day' Trump protest | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad Thousands to take to the streets for 'not my Presidents' Day' protests against Trump- with many demanding the President's IMPEACHMENT Tens of thousands of people are due to protest against Trump in 28 different cities across the US on Monday The largest of the many demonstrations will take place in New York City, Los Angeles and Chicago 'Not My President's Day' events were organized on social media and are calling for Trump to be impeached They come after a weekend of protests against Trump's stance on science and his immigration ban Published: 14:34 GMT, 20 February 2017 | Updated: 15:53 GMT, 20 February 2017 46 shares
